title: weelife

creator: XF Game Inc
descriptionHtml:
"Weelife provides a beautiful and extraordinary 3D virtual world for everyone! In Weelife, you can shape and dress up your own avatar, use these avatars to explore hundreds of interesting rooms. In these rooms, you can chat with your friends and play together.

FEATURES
character image
- Free design of 3D character appearance image
- Custom design of facial features
- Variety of hairstyles can be matched at will
-Hundreds of fashion outfits to wear

voice social
-Join the room and open the microphone to communicate with each other
- Add friends, chat with private messages
- High-quality social environment, expand your social circle

room function
- A variety of room templates, and you can create your own exclusive room
-Share & publish the room to invite more friends to join the room
-Join hot rooms and meet more new friends
-Play interactive games in the room to enjoy fun of social

SPECIAL FEATURES
Friends Square
-Real-time display of friends' character images, showing personal charm
-Display your recent status and share your mood dynamics with your friends

simple application
While offering an unprecedented range of features, great care has been taken to keep the interface simple. Through the novice guide, you will know how to play it in one minute.

privacy security
We take your privacy very seriously and will never allow any third parties to access your data. You can delete any messages you've ever sent or received for both parties at any time without leaving a trace. Weelife will never use your data to show you ads.

Want to meet more new friends? Say hello, and everyone can be your friend! Weelife is a great place to make friends and to relax. Don't hesitate, come to weelife to experience a different life!

Have any questions about Weelife (with in-app features like character design and room editor). Please contact us via .
Facebook: Weelife
Instagram: Weelife.official
Discord: https://discord.gg/6nacMA6bWB"
